section(class="template-wrapper act_6" )
    aside(class="template-asideLeft o-aside-Item")

    |
    |
    div(class="template-section m-a")
        section(class="template-content" )
            h5 Listen to the news report and complete the following activities.
            .row.row-flex.justify-between.align-items-center
                .col.xs12.md8.col-center
                    audio(controls class='row')
                        source(src='unit_2/module_8/assets/audios/act_6_1.mp3' type='audio/mpeg')
                        | Your browser does not support the audio element.
                    |
                    .c-cardGreen
                        .c-cardGreenContent.ta-c
                            h5 Movies that empower women
                            h6 Breena Kerr posted Jan 27, 2017

                            p Read the full story here: #[a(href="http://www.yesmagazine.org/happiness/10-films-to-keep-you-inspired-after-the-womens-march-20170127" target="blank")  www.yesmagazine.org]
                    |
            h5 Now choose the best answer.
            .row.row-flex.justify-between
                .col.xs12.md5: .row.row-flex.align-items-center
                    .row.mt30
                        .row
                            p #[strong.u-textColor_4 •] The intention of the article is to...

                        .row
                            input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_1" id="selInput_1" value="1")
                            label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_1") Entertain Women.
                            input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_1" id="selInput_2" value="2")
                            label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_2") Suggest entertainment for the women.
                            input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_1" id="selInput_3" value="3")
                            label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_3") Keep subject matter alive.
                    .row.mt30
                        .row
                            h6 #[strong.u-textColor_4 •] Choose true or false.
                            p  Frida Kahlo was played by Salma Hayek.
                        div(class="row row-flex justify-around")
                            input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_2" id="selInput_4" value="1")
                            label(class="c-Checkbox w45" for="selInput_4") True
                            input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_2" id="selInput_5" value="2")
                            label(class="c-Checkbox w45" for="selInput_5") False
                    .row.mt30
                        .row
                            p #[strong.u-textColor_4 •] Complete the sentence.
                            p The movie about a boy who becomes a feminist is called #[input(type="text" readonly class="c-input" ng-model="txtcaptura_a")] .
                        .row
                            input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_3" id="selInput_6" value="1")
                            label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_6" ng-click="txtcaptura_a = '20th Century Women.'") 20th Century Women.
                            input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_3" id="selInput_7" value="2")
                            label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_7" ng-click="txtcaptura_a = 'Mustang.'") Mustang.
                            input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_3" id="selInput_8" value="3")
                            label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_8" ng-click="txtcaptura_a = 'Whale Rider.'") Whale Rider.
                |
                .col.xs12.md5
                    .row.mt30
                        .row
                            p #[strong.u-textColor_4 •] Fill in the blank space with the appropriate person.
                            p The main character in the movie called Whale Rider is #[input(type="text" readonly class="c-input" ng-model="txtcaptura_b")] .

                        .row
                            input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_4" id="selInput_9" value="1")
                            label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_9" ng-click="txtcaptura_b = 'Stellarly.'") Stellarly.
                            input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_4" id="selInput_10" value="2")
                            label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_10" ng-click="txtcaptura_b = 'Pai.'") Pai.
                            input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_4" id="selInput_11" value="3")
                            label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_11" ng-click="txtcaptura_b = 'Frida Kahlo.'") Frida Kahlo.
                    .row.mt30
                        .row
                            p #[strong.u-textColor_4 •] Boys Don’t Cry is about...
                        .row
                            input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_5" id="selInput_12" value="1")
                            label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_12") An abused boy in Nebraska.
                            input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_5" id="selInput_13" value="2")
                            label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_13") A man that was born as a woman.
                            input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_5" id="selInput_14" value="3")
                            label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_14") A woman that was born as a man.
